          "id": "chapter-1-arrival",
          "title": "Impossible Memory",
          "paragraphs": [
            "At the morgue, Elian aligns reflections from a bloodless aristocrat's final memory. The completed perspective reveals a donor entering the cathedral dispensary after the records say she died.",
            "When the contradictory recollections tear free of the page, they become The Last-Memory Wraith. Elian must hold one truthful image in place long enough to preserve the dispensary seal."
          ],
          "semanticLabel": "Elian assembles floating memory fragments above a rain-dark morgue table.",
          "actionLabel": "Reconstruct the memory"
        }
      ]
    },
