        {
          "id": "chapter-2-arrival",
          "title": "The Marked Donor",
          "paragraphs": [
            "Elian follows the donor mark through burial lists, night-clinic appointments, and pages replaced with immaculate forgeries. Sister Anja risks her post to smuggle out the original register and the names of families still waiting for answers.",
            "Ink and sealing wax gather around the stolen pages as The Redaction Hart, an antlered guardian trained to gore inconvenient names from history. Defeating it leaves one unaltered address: Mirelle Dane's shuttered laboratory."
