          "title": "A Hunger Measured",
          "paragraphs": [
            "Elian corners Mirelle in her ruined laboratory and finds her measuring each pulse of hunger instead of feeding it. To prove her treatment works, they must recalibrate an assay sabotaged to label every infected patient incurable.",
            "The spoiled samples knit into The Veinroot Colony, feeding on fear as quickly as blood. Elian protects Mirelle while she names every false result, and their reluctant partnership survives its first honest test."
          ],
          "semanticLabel": "Mirelle steadies a silver blood assay while Elian watches in a crimson-lit laboratory.",
          "actionLabel": "Calibrate the assay"
        }
