          "title": "The Staged Hunt",
          "paragraphs": [
            "A vampire attack erupts during a crowded charity procession, exactly where the dispensary's warnings predicted. Elian notices that its blood fragments repeat memories from earlier victims, proving the supposed attacker was planted and conditioned for the scene.",
            "Above the panicked square, The Rehearsal Gargoyle echoes each practiced scream and drives the crowd toward a second captive. Elian and Mirelle break its script in time to save the captive alive, denying Bellgrave the monster it expected to see."
          ],
          "semanticLabel": "Elian and Mirelle protect a charity procession beneath a winged stone creature.",
          "actionLabel": "Break the staged attack"
