          "title": "The Benefactor's Arithmetic",
          "paragraphs": [
            "Anja's stolen records connect Provost Absal Rook's longevity patients to cycles of infection, fear, and disappearance. Every charitable donation becomes a variable in a program that enriches memory in blood before selling it to Bellgrave's most powerful families.",
            "The figures rise from the ledger as The Tithe Constellation, a cold geometry that reduces each victim to yield and cost. By restoring names to its numbered stars, the investigators reveal Rook's reservoir beneath the cathedral."
          ],
          "semanticLabel": "Names and crimson figures form a constellation above Rook's secret account books.",
          "actionLabel": "Balance the true ledger"
        }
      ]
