          "title": "The Public Ledger",
          "paragraphs": [
            "By noon, the dispensary steps are covered with copied records that no single office can destroy. Families find the missing, patients receive Mirelle's treatment, and Rook faces the city without a charitable title to hide behind.",
            "Elian adds his own hunting reports to the archive, including every conclusion he drew too quickly. Evidence, he decides, should expose certainty as readily as monsters."
