          "paragraphs": [
            "Anja opens the former dispensary as a clinic governed by patients and donors, with Mirelle directing its research in full view of the public. No one is asked to surrender a memory to earn care.",
            "When rain returns to Bellgrave, Elian and Mirelle walk into it together toward a new case. This time, hunter and physician begin with a question instead of a verdict."
          ],
